Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3-all, python3-pytest (>= 9) <!nocheck>, python3-pytest-mpl <!nocheck>, python3-setuptools, python3-setuptools-scm, python3-typing-extensions
Description: Saves and loads to the cache a transformed versions of a source object A robust and extensible package to cache on disk the result of expensive calculations. . When the source is changed, the DiskCache detects that the cached file is older, calls `parse` again storing and returning the new result. . It is also possible to detect that the file has changed by hashing the file by using `DiskCacheByHash` instead of `DiskCacheByMTime`. . Cached files are saved using the pickle protocol, and each has a companion json file with the header content.
